HEADWORD: Suffossion
<hw>Suf*fos"sion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>suffossio</ets>, from <ets>suffodere</ets>, <ets>suffossum</ets>,
to dig under; <ets>sub</ets> under + <ets>fodere</ets> to dig.]</ety>
<def>A digging under; an undermining.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>
<rj><au>Bp. Hall.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
